Hi All,

ApacheCon Asia is coming again as a virtual event this July 29 - 31.
The CFP will end on Tuesday, May 31st, 2022 8:00 AM (Beijing time -
UTC +8).

More details could be found here:

https://apachecon.com/acasia2022/cfp.html

Please remember that there is no need to be present at the conference,
it is completely virtual,
the talk is pre-recorded.

The presentation could be either in English or in Chinese.

Please free free to submit your ideas related to Web server / Tomcat
or other topics here:

https://shimo.im/forms/6ZTBLanjqW8pY3dj/fill?channel=website

--
Best Regards！
Huxing
